To calculate the expected return for each asset class, the investment team first researched the historical total returns of the index or similar asset class underlying the ETFs (fee and currency adjusted). kidsInfo.en-en: The projected future values shown for the Raiz Kids Accounts are hypothetical in nature and should not be relied on. They may be affected by inaccurate market return assumptions or market risks and uncertainties and will differ materially from results ultimately achieved. In order to calculate the expected return for each asset class, the investment team first researched the historical total returns of the index or similar asset class underlying the ETFs (fee and currency adjusted). For the IVV, IEU, 30 years of historical data was used to calculate the return. For the STW 20 years of historical data was used for the IAA, IAF, RCB 10 years of historic information was used. An interest rate of 2.5% and inflation rate of 2% were assumed. For RARI and ETHI their was no historic information available and the investment team made an educated guess based on similar asset classes. All returns are deflated for inflation. Factors that can cause significant variation from the historic risks are outlined in the product disclosure statement.

executingDescription.en-en:
This is reflected in the fact that just 1 in 8 young Australians feel they are not in a good savings position, and just 1 in 3 have a savings plan that is working.

Why?

Not only is there a lack of savings tools available but there are a number of barriers that stop people from building an effective investment portfolio. High brokerage fees, minimum investments, and often a knowledge barrier, stops everyday people from getting started on investing early and making the most of the stock market.

Financial experts suggest that to be successful at saving money, it is important to make it a part of your lifestyle. This involves behaving in ways that help you save regularly such as putting money aside from eachpaycheck, saving small amounts (petty cash) as often as possible, keeping regular track of your spending, and so on.

Below is one solution that you can use to grow your financial potential.

investSpareChangeDescription.en-en:
With Raiz, I can get fully invested into a diversified portfolio of ETFs and/or Bitcoin with as little as {currency_symbol}5. Raiz has several portfolio options, including the ability to build your own portfolio and one with Bitcoin. The portfolio options allow you to choose an investment suitable for you at many different levels of risk.

With no brokerage, contribution or withdrawal fees, and an understandable fee model, Raiz proves that investing doesn’t have to be expensive or confusing.

There are 3 easy ways to save and invest, (1) Using lump sums you can invest anytime with any amount. (2) Using recurring deposits, you can automate your investments to stick to a savings plan and set a savings goal. (3) Using round-ups, you save and invest every time you spend money; Raiz rounds up every purchase to the nearest dollar and invests the virtual change into your portfolio.

investSpareChangeDescription.id-id:
Pernahkah kita berpikir bahwa kita selalu diajarkan untuk menabung hanya untuk memenuhi hasrat atau keinginan semata? Kita hanya terpaksa menabung, karena ada yang ingin kita miliki. Terkadang kita lupa tujuan besar dari kegiatan menabung dan kita lupa bahwa hidup ini penuh dengan ketidakpastian.

Kegiatan menabung semakin lama memang semakin mudah untuk diucapkan daripada dilakukan. Wajar saja terjadi karena kebutuhan kita pun bertambah sedangkan banyak pengorbanan yang harus dilakukan untuk menambah pendapatan.Salah satu quote dari buku The Richest Man in Babylon mengatakan bahwa kita tidak boleh lupa menyisihkan sebagian pendapatan kita untuk “membayar diri kita sendiri”. Membayar dalam quote tersebut adalah untuk keberlangsungan hidup kita dimasa mendatang, contohnya kebutuhan darurat seperti kran bocor, ban motor pecah, dinding bocor, atau mungkin untuk memenuhi kebutuhan sehari-hari ketika kita kehilangan pekerjaan. Masih ingat bagaimana pandemi memorak porandakan kehidupan kita bukan?

Membentuk kebiasaan menabung artinya kita butuh keberanian untuk mengorbankan hal-hal yang tidak begitu mendesak. Langkah pertama memang selalu berat untuk dilakukan. Namun jika tidak dilakukan sekarang, tentunya kita bisa saja kehilangan kesempatan untuk menikmati hidup yang lebih baik.

Kita bisa memulai langkah pertama kebiasaan menabung dengan jumlah yang kecil dan rutin. Raiz Indonesia memiliki fitur Recurring yang membantu kita untuk menjadwalkan investasi secara rutin dan otomatis dimulai dari Rp10.000,00.

Jadi, kapan kita mau ambil langkah pertama kita untuk memulai kebiasaan menabung?

rollingOver.en-en: Rolling over your superannuation means you are subject to the performance of your Raiz Invest Super fund and are no longer exposed to risks and benefits of your pre-existing superannuation fund. Theserisks are outlined in the Raiz Invest Super PDS. It also means you forfeit rights to any insurance or benefits assosiated with those pre-existing superannuation funds including life insurance, total and permanent disability, income protection. If you are uncertain you should contact your existing super provider for information about any fees that may apply, or any other information about the effect this transfer may have on your benefits. You may also wish to seek independent financial advice before making this decision.
